10:10 The impact of 'expectations' versus reality.
`____ `__ `_____ `_ `_____________ `_____ `_______ 
#HSBC share price fall provides a reminder that in the short term, actual results are usually less important than the comparison of results to 'expectations'. It is very difficult to make money this way. Better to focus on valuation and the long term drivers of profit growth. -- Dan Kemp (@Dan_the_analyst).
