Some of the most interesting parts of the results aren't even in the finances, but in the six-page legal section..
`___ `_ `__ `___ `__________ `____ `_ `__ `______ `_____ `___ `_ `__ `________ `__ `_ `__ `_______ `____ `________ 
'A full six pages of the results release were dedicated to updates on litigation and legal proceedings, an overhang from past misdeeds that the bank is yet to entirely draw a line under..
